it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.match

Class Match

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.match.Match
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlayerDiedListener, PlayerOverkilledListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class Match
extends java.lang.Object
implements PlayerDiedListener, PlayerOverkilledListener
    This class represents the match, which is the core of the model and contains all the information relative to the game status
